de.tototec.utils.functional

Class FList

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.tototec.utils.functional.FList

  • public abstract class FList
extends Object

    Collection of static methods that mostly produce Lists and accept Iterables or Java arrays. Method mkString(Iterable, String) produces a String.
